---
title: Chermoula Pumpkin & Nutty Couscous Salad with Plant-Based Parsley-Garlic Aioli
description: Who knew a sunset could taste so good? Roasted pumpkin and many other veggies bring the comfort of those toasty
roast flavours. Spice the veggies with chermoula and sprinkle in a herby garlic seasoning then toss through a soft
couscous to bring all the warm colours and tastes together. There’s even a note of nuttiness from the almonds!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

